_header: Behold and see how that nature
_description: James Ryman, A carol on the Miraculous Conception — nine quatrains (aaab) and burden (bbbc): ‘Ecce quod natura / mutat sua iura / Virgo parit pura / dei filium’

CULEe112.First Lines:
Beholde & see how that natureChaungith here lawe a mayden
                    pure…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…As the sonne beame goth thurgh the glasThat mayde full of
                    honour
